{"tid":526993,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"比人整濕左部電腦 但條撚樣唔還錢（ 7 ）","createTime":"2018-01-12T07:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T18:11:46.000Z","uid":100775,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8dab31be35a18f589f6bdc1ace1429b97eccc1ad","tid":526993,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>hkcc Social Science-NS Year 1楊匡文 Bryan Yeung <br />\n半樽茶倒落人地部新買嘅macbook 唔撚賠錢 <br />\n<br />\n當初係佢話要考埋midterm 先處理<br />\n好啦 我等 <br />\nMidterm 完左 再問佢 佢又已讀不回<br />\n話星期六晚唔得閒喇喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/222901_97ce5cae22cbddaa7256eaeca1e80934.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F222901_97ce5cae22cbddaa7256eaeca1e80934.png&h=1af04cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如是者 我等到躁 就話告小額錢債啦<br />\n係佢贊成去小額錢債 又話肯比地址嘅 但而家又唔肯比<br />\n又嫌我搵個個整電腦嘅師傅唔夠專業 <br />\n話係我部電腦本身有問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/215948_3f0addecae9c169a81fcc0f79f0419a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F215948_3f0addecae9c169a81fcc0f79f0419a1.png&h=68a817f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我咪去搵apple 囉 夠專業喇掛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/200900_bcf6e3b90c66ff7f1541266d84950111.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F200900_bcf6e3b90c66ff7f1541266d84950111.jpeg&h=4d1b9cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁因為個維修費唔同左 <br />\n而我之前同佢講 佢又冇表示喎 <br />\n所以去到Exam Period 前兩個禮拜（29/11) 我再面對面問佢想點 <br />\n佢又話要翻屋企諗下先再答我<br />\n結果我等等等等 等左個幾月 就忍唔住再問佢啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/223400_01785ce287aa5c9de0cff3caa0269c0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F223400_01785ce287aa5c9de0cff3caa0269c0d.png&h=64d99408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果佢係話一蚊都唔賠<br />\n<br />\n仲話我屈佢錢喎 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/200850_782357d1b9aa93b5320608767731844a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F200850_782357d1b9aa93b5320608767731844a.jpeg&h=4e4193c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識佢嘅人 請認清呢個人</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n幫手開既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee92967b8fac264f643c759157eb266ae63c615","tid":526993,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7224b5fc018a92bf9cba43fd60ab0260c5523da","tid":526993,"uid":69939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:58:31.000Z","msg":"開到（7）啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4f39d85bfa413f7430ae98675fcc8efca2d323","tid":526993,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee92967b8fac264f643c759157eb266ae63c615","tid":526993,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"有兩個咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我搵唔到先開"},{"pid":"39f5429c72eb2f832bf1d3460282cf748109f8c3","tid":526993,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aee28d86b1e9e6de62ab8ab2f1e0a871aa6a3a0e","tid":526993,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f5429c72eb2f832bf1d3460282cf748109f8c3","tid":526993,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f4f39d85bfa413f7430ae98675fcc8efca2d323","tid":526993,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee92967b8fac264f643c759157eb266ae63c615","tid":526993,"uid"